The '''Red Mushroom''' is found in [[the Mines]], via [[foraging]] in the [[Secret Woods]] in the [[Summer]] and (more rarely) [[Fall]], grown in the [[The Cave|The Farm Cave]] if the mushroom option is chosen, on the farm in fall if the [[Farm Maps|Forest Farm Map]] has been chosen, or from a [[Tapper|tapped]] [[Mushroom Tree]].  It may also be occasionally found in [[Garbage Can]]s, at the [[Traveling Cart]], or in the [[Ginger Island#Dig Site|Ginger Island mushroom cave]].

